# PRD: InvoiceIt

InvoiceIt is a light and fast inventory managment system and invoice maker
It allows users to create and add product invoice & customer and other 

# Experience

## Dashboard 

the dashboard Shows : 

Total Invoice Created  
Total of Sales 
Total Cutomer
out of stock product 
recent invoices 

## Product 

the Product window will allow users to set the name ,qt ,price of the product 
& show the list of existing once in the inventory  


## Customer 

the Customer window will allow users to set the name ,phone number & other detail abot the customer 
& show the list of existing one in the System    

## Invoice

Invoices can be created for existing Customer with the Existing product list & edited with abilty to custom the Output 

# Users

there will be two types of users (Admin , Manager ) with diffrent access to the app functionality 
